chunks.text: When you go joyriding, which student would you like to end up like?
The one who is paralysed from the legs down.
The one with the broken rest.
The one with glass in their head.
Or the one who's unconscious and never wakes up.
I don't want to do this at all, but everyone else is going, so is it really that bad if I go? I got you.
We should into going out with friends on the restricted when they know that it's illegal.
